data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the heart of tranquility and right in the epicenter of New Braunfels charm!! This enchanting Spanish-style residence, nestled on a cul-de-sac in a well-established neighborhood, offers the perfect blend of comfort and style. Featuring 3 bedrooms and 2 baths, this residence sits on a generous .36-acre lot, a stone's throw away from Gruene, Schlitterbahn and the Guadalupe River. Step inside to discover a home adorned with tiled floors and an inviting kitchen, creating a warm and welcoming atmosphere. The heart of this home, the kitchen, is a culinary haven where memories are made. Picture yourself entertaining guests or preparing delightful meals in this tastefully designed space. One of the many highlights of this property is the massively oversized covered back patio that promises serene moments with no backyard neighbors. Imagine unwinding in your private jacuzzi, surrounded by lush greenery and the soothing ambiance of nature. This home goes above and beyond with its unique features, including a detached, temperature-controlled room. This versatile space opens up possibilities—use it as a separate detached room for guests, a home gym, or a home office for maximum productivity. Venture into the lavish backyard, where an enclosed raised garden bed awaits your green thumb, a greenhouse-style building provides the perfect sanctuary for your plants, as well as a shed for ample storage space for your outdoor essentials. This backyard oasis is an extension of the home's charm, offering a serene escape from the everyday hustle and bustle. Embrace the lifestyle you've always envisioned in this Spanish style gem. With its ideal location, thoughtful features, and expansive outdoor haven, this residence is not just a home; it's an experience. Seize the opportunity to make this dream home yours and embark on a journey of comfort, style, and endless possibilities. This home is a must see!
